Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}预定于上海和平国际会议场召开为期两天的反恐国际合作会议…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大泽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你闹什么别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也没必要不让人进门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我换衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你换的太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经一点了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我换的是宫廷礼服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各国首脑自昨天起陆续抵达浦东国际机场…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南是个普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论她有着怎样的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论她过着怎样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这 只是我在自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时 迦南她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又要失去什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下面还没看过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强自己去看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不该看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不用看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青色的火焰 燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从今以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意压枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与多名敌人枪战时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向最接近的敌人连射两发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有命中 也要以脚趾为轴转身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击下一个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让对方近身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪的性能是固定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪械会使战士的能力平均化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进一步讲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不选择符合当前水平的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会被第一个淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最先要记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是手里的武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它没有颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太阳是青色的 我讨厌它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是憎恨的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有青色的气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里就肯定有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这性能超乎想象了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是什么颜色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆的颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是淡咖啡色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡咖啡色？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周不洗澡的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任谁都能看出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点疼都忍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说还是个新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你已经经历多少战场了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该疼时还是会疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要勉强自己做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是家人的 标志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望之地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因谁而失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没能成为你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随处可见的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在想着复仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冤冤相报没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须用义务对抗仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则无法得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全都知道 夏姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大泽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也该给我开门…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不换宫廷礼服了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是放弃打扮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主编教过我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨好女人要先讨好她的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这么简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人心 海底针啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 这样可没法抓住奈奈的芳心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不想抓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两年前 所有村民都突然失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公安部想掩盖这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么反恐国际会议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能忘记消失的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能容许公安部为所欲为！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛮有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不像NGO的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算演那种猴戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CIA的人也不会去看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像事不关己一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓报酬 只有立功的人才有资格收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以看成是将来立功的订金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将来只会变成日式夜店的色老头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要抹杀过去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你抹杀的村庄一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之既然失败了 我就不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个愚者还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你心中盛开的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这个给她买条项链吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 我会在床上取悦她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾为谁而失去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又将为谁而失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们喝水就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身心融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然会产生如此和谐的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想说蟹黄蟹肉很对味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也太诗意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人好少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是淡季嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上海秋季才产蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还能更好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在都是养殖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差距没这么大…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实先生不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在很多地方打过工…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她是个贫乳来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她打了几份工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个国家贫乳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 贫富差距比较大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什么是普通的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满自信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭那份存在感就能压服众人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况之下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值此NBCR
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反恐国际合作会议在上海召开之际
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能被主办国中国选为警备合作对象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们大太公司无上的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位女士是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说是大太公司的大股东
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是原中东著名王侯的独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气质果然不同凡响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可不是日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的朋友一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 尽量不要往暗处走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万不能去上海站北边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器… 没有是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带上相机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以拿闪光灯闪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 千晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到符合标志的团体了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 画质太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用数码相机拍的底片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但主编说了些有趣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说比起标志 更像凸起的血管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血管…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御法川！ 偷什么懒呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追加采访！ 马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血管以相同的形状浮现…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你好好高兴一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南… 见面又能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:15:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我伤害了她？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每当我遇险时 迦南都会来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这次也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我端起相机的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我遇到了迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了正视那些未知的事物 曾被自己无视的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了去了解迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在耍什么脾气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她之所以开枪 全是为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却一心想要逃避罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从心底某处责备着迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}哎 不允许拍 不允许拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}这不能给人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用自己双眼去看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的心去判断！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会对真相视而不见的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}我要把那玩意塞进你耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}打得你满地找牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}看你还废话不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我不会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为大泽玛丽亚是迦南的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}不是说了吗 不许拍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是迦南的… 好朋友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀呀呀 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工拖了一会儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}对不起对不起 谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等… 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天吃毛蟹的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可不是你的祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一带很乱 不要再接近了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽玛丽亚 是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的事 迦南的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都想知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现一个世界奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体验过恐惧的人 不会为仇恨所动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南和你我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我堕落到同一水平线上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神里充满了仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的反应变慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的你 没有这么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算在我杀了夏姆之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为憎恨而战的感觉如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像泥潭一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越是挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越会陷入那无尽的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忍过了那份屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经爬上岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得好听…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你看个证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还能成长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀你
